</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">At Wired last week, Andy Greenberg had=
 a <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/27330343.276596=
/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud2lyZWQuY29tL3N0b3J5L3RyYWNlcnMtaW4tdGhlLWRhcmstd2VsY29tZS=
