1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-c=
olor: #ccc;">gripping and upsetting story</a> about how law enforcement bro=
ught down a child pornography website that accepted payment in cryptocurren=
cy, which made its proprietor and users fairly=C2=A0easy to trace. One inte=
resting note=C2=A0is that the investigation started because some Internal R=
evenue Service agents were bored and=C2=A0started looking around the blockc=
hain for crimes:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">At loose ends =
in Bangkok, Gambaryan and Janczewski spent much of their time idly contempl=
ating what their next case should be, browsing through Chainalysis=E2=80=99=
 blockchain-tracing software Reactor to brainstorm ideas. Dark-web markets =
like AlphaBay seemed to have been reduced to a shambles by the Thailand ope=
ration, and they=E2=80=99d take months or even years to recover. The agents=
 considered taking on a dark-web gambling site. But illegal online casinos =
hardly seemed worth their attention. ...</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">St=
uck in the terminal with hours to kill, they sat half-awake and bored, lite=
rally staring at the wall. To pass the hours, Gambaryan decided to try call=
ing Chainalysis=E2=80=99 Levin to discuss next cases. When Levin picked up =
the phone, he had news to share. He=E2=80=99d been looking into a website t=
hat didn=E2=80=99t fit among the IRS=E2=80=99s usual targets but that he ho=
ped they=E2=80=99d be willing to check out: Welcome to Video.</p></blockquo=
te><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">It=E2=80=99s not just that, if you do crime=
s using Bitcoin, the public immutable blockchain makes it easier for author=
ities to find you. It=E2=80=99s that so many people do so many crimes using=
 Bitcoin, and so many of them are not good at covering their tracks,=C2=A0t=
hat browsing the public immutable blockchain is a good way for the authorit=
ies to discover crimes they hadn=E2=80=99t even thought of before.=C2=A0</p=
